<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Recovery Status Update — Case {{ case_id }}</title>
{% include "_styles.html.j2" %}
</head>
<body>

<section class="cover">
  <div class="cover-letterhead">
    <div class="cover-wordmark">
      Recupero
      <span class="tagline">Investigation Services</span>
    </div>
    <div class="cover-letterhead-right">
      <div class="confidential">Confidential — Client Update</div>
      <div class="date">{{ generated_at }} UTC</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="cover-title-block">
    <div class="cover-eyebrow">Week {{ week_number }} Status</div>
    <h1>Recovery<br/>Status Update</h1>
    <p class="cover-subtitle">
      {{ days_since_engagement }} days into the active recovery
      engagement. This is your scheduled weekly status update under
      our 30-day reporting commitment.
    </p>
    <div class="cover-rule"></div>
  </div>

  <dl class="cover-meta">
    <div class="cover-meta-item">
      <dt>Client</dt>
      <dd>{{ victim.name }}</dd>
    </div>
    <div class="cover-meta-item">
      <dt>Case Reference</dt>
      <dd>{{ case_id }}</dd>
    </div>
    <div class="cover-meta-item">
      <dt>Engagement Started</dt>
      <dd>{{ engagement_started_human }}</dd>
    </div>
    <div class="cover-meta-item">
      <dt>Remaining in 30-day Window</dt>
      <dd>{{ days_remaining }} days</dd>
    </div>
  </dl>
</section>

<h2>1. Where things stand</h2>
<div class="summary-box">
  <p style="margin:0;">
    {{ status_summary_paragraph }}
  </p>
</div>

<h2>2. Actions taken since engagement started</h2>
{% if recent_actions %}
<table class="evidence">
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th style="width:11em;">Date (UTC)</th>
      <th>Action</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    {% for action in recent_actions %}
    <tr>
      <td class="mono">{{ action.timestamp }}</td>
      <td>{{ action.description }}</td>
    </tr>
    {% endfor %}
  </tbody>
</table>
{% else %}
<p>
  Recupero is preparing to send the compliance freeze letters and
  law-enforcement handoff package. The first sends will go out
  within the 5-business-day commitment of the engagement letter.
</p>
{% endif %}

{% if compliance_responses %}
<h2>3. Compliance team responses</h2>
<table class="evidence">
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>Issuer</th>
      <th>Status</th>
      <th>Notes</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    {% for resp in compliance_responses %}
    <tr>
      <td>{{ resp.issuer }}</td>
      <td>{{ resp.status }}</td>
      <td class="small">{{ resp.notes }}</td>
    </tr>
    {% endfor %}
  </tbody>
</table>
{% endif %}

<h2>{% if compliance_responses %}4{% else %}3{% endif %}. What's next this week</h2>
<ul>
  {% for item in next_steps %}
  <li>{{ item }}</li>
  {% endfor %}
</ul>

<h2>{% if compliance_responses %}5{% else %}4{% endif %}. Anything you'd like to flag?</h2>
<p>
  If you've had direct communication with any law-enforcement
  officer, attorney, or compliance team about this case since our
  last update — or if you've noticed any new on-chain activity
  related to the affected wallet — please reply to this email and
  let us know. It helps us coordinate.
</p>
<p>
  As a reminder: this engagement covers our work through
  {{ engagement_closes_human }}. After that date, this case
  transitions to a no-charge follow-up status — we remain
  available for clarification questions and will reach out if
  material developments occur (e.g., an issuer enforcement action,
  a court-appointed restitution program), but the weekly status
  cadence ends.
</p>


<div class="signature-block">
  <p style="margin:0 0 var(--space-md);">
    Best regards,
  </p>
  <div class="signature-fields">
    <strong>{{ investigator.name }}</strong>
    Investigator of record · {{ investigator.email }}
  </div>
</div>


<footer class="brief-footer">
  <div class="footer-brand">Recupero · Investigation Services</div>
  <div class="footer-meta">
    <code>Followup-W{{ week_number }} {{ case_id }}</code><br/>
    Generated {{ generated_at }} UTC · v{{ software_version }}<br/>
    <span class="confidential">Confidential.</span> Intended for {{ victim.name }}.
  </div>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
